definitions.definition: Extremely subtle or refined ; extremely sensitive to slight impressions or perceptions.
Extremely refined or sophisticated ; very elegant .
Having an especially fine size or texture ; made of very small particles or threads.
examples: Some recipes call for superfine sugar because it dissolves easier.

definitions.definition: Of a very high or pure grade or quality .
